      "id": "r002",
      "type": "factual",
      "topic": "architecture",
      "content": "Node.js fs.watch uses OS-level file notifications (FSEvents on macOS, inotify on Linux). For watching a single file like claims.json, it is sufficient without chokidar. Zero dependencies needed.",
      "source": {
