      "type": "recommendation",
      "topic": "ux-pattern",
      "content": "For the compiler passes, use a linear pipeline stepper (like GitHub Actions) — stages shown left-to-right with status icons (pending/running/done/error). Color coding: green=pass, yellow=running, red=fail, grey=pending.",
